text: Jean-Yves Touzaint (born 8 October 1948) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
